The enterprises "AktobeMunaymaskomplex" and "Stroйдеtal" will maintain the 7 percent rate.
The salaries of Kazakhstan Oil and Petroleum Equipment Plant will be increased by 5 percent.
The positive trends will take place in the institutions of "Kaspieneft" and "Transenergo".
In total, these enterprises employ 7.5 thousand people.
The salaries of 4,2 thousand of them will be increased by an average of 7% from the new year.
Today, the issue of raising the wages of workers is being considered in 30 more enterprises.
