College leaders are deceiving the country and the government.
The prosecutor's office of East Kazakhstan region conducted an investigation into the activities of colleges in the region and identified numerous violations of the law, as well as the facts of misuse of budget funds.
In particular, during the placement of the state order, there were identified cases of non-compliance with the tender procedures, false teaching of students, illegal grant award, non-compliance of teachers with the qualification requirements, non-provision of students with dormitories, as well as income from illegal renting of state property.
It is often the case that the administration of educational institutions does not provide assistance in the employment of graduates by artificially increasing the number of graduates employed.
Despite the violation of the rules of placement of the state educational order, namely, the absence of accommodation for students from other places, the education department of the region annually granted grants to the business and service college of Semipalatinsk, the polytechnic college of Ayagoz and two colleges in Ust-Kamenogorsk.
The college administration included in the price of student accommodation in the hostel the costs for the public services included in the total amount of the contract, rented rooms in the hostels to third parties.
He has deceived 12 students at the college in Karsum.
Teachers and industrial teachers evaluated these students in theoretical and practical study journals during the course, sent them to interim certification, transferred them from course to course.
In addition, the total amount of damage caused to the state by the scholarships paid to these students amounted to 8 million tenge.
The investigation is ongoing.
The facts of illegal use of property for private purposes were also identified on the territory of the college .
For example, on the territory of East Kazakhstan regional art school named after the brothers Abdulinders, folk artists, there is a long-term paid parking.
After the proposal of the prosecutor, the parking lot is planned to be closed and a sports field will be built in its place.
According to the results of the investigation , prosecutors determined damage amounting to more than 43 million tenge .
So far , 36 million tenge have been collected according to the control acts .
60 persons were brought to disciplinary responsibility and 4 persons to administrative responsibility.
